Package: pneumatools
Title: Pneumatron Data Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(c("Gabriel", "S."), "Pires", , "gabriel.slpires@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5354-1957"))
Description: This package provides tools for analyzing Pneumatron data,
    useful in plant hydraulic studies. It includes functions for data
    processing and a user-friendly dashboard for interactive analysis,
    enabling users to perform complex analyses without needing to program.
